title: Sarah's Story
description: Sarah Beauchamp has made a life for herself in the past having given up on returning to the present. She only has one question – What had happened?Captain Matthew Barrington is determined to find the longest missing agent – Sarah. She was lost when the Time Displacement Unit exploded.The Time Displacement Corps greatest fear is causing a Paradox. But when an agent has been missing for ten years, can they avoid it?
author: Delilah K. Stephans
